SMASH CANNON PREFAB
----------------------------

This is a cannon which I made for mg_run_fetboy_run (http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/89869) & mg_smash_cannonsz (http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/89630)

The cannons fire func_physblocks out every few seconds when you left click. The cannon is player controlled and you have to press 'e' on the button to take control.

Please feel free to use this prefab but give credit where used!

Thanks Paul_Deagle (aka [SG] Paul)
